(66122, 'I did not High Priestess, we have grim tidings from my homeland. As you know it has been held by the Scourge ever since it''s fall. The Sunwell perverted by the vile magics of Kel''thuzad.', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(66123, 'However, the Thalassian pass has recently been swarming with Undead pushing south, and our mages have felt the taint of Fel in the region. I worked with Ranger-Lord Hawkspear to send a scouting party into the region.Out of twelve rangers, only two returned.', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(66124, '"However, what those two witnessed was not something we could ignore. The Scourge is amassing it''s army for an invasion in the south, and the northern region of Quel''thalas is swarming with demons."', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(66125, 'Even the Rangers, unattuned to magic, could feel the sway of the Fel in the air. We suspect the Sunwell has been tainted with fel, possibly it has even become a portal to summon demons.', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(66126, 'They are not attacking the Scourge yet. We surmise that they''re either allied or the Demons are preparing for the offensive.', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(66127, 'What?! Are you certain of this?! Once again your ways bring doom upon this world Highborne!', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
